title: Caitlyn Jenner's 'I Am Cait' renewed for season 2 - WAPT-TV Jackson
text:
With word coming Thursday that Caitlyn Jenner's reality TV series "I Am Cait" has been renewed for a second season, take a look back at the life of the former Olympian and reality television star so far. "I Am Cait," the docuseries starring Caitlyn Jenner, has been renewed for a second season by E!, the network announced on Thursday.
 WAPT-TV Jackson.
